   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting" image="QN_Npc_Genaral_Duglas.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The battle where the Black Dragon appeared?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther${action:talk}<BR>Oh, I heard you also participated in this battle, that took place at the <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Overlord's Gate</FONT>.<BR>I heard <FONT color=#a82424>General Douglas</FONT> and the elite soldiers were very brave.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-b" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Oh... You were also there, so you must have seen it.<BR>If the word gets out that <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT> is back, people might be frightened, so the Royal Castle deemed it to be secret.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-c" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(So the Royal Castle took care of that.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Even if they keep it a secret, some day the word will go out. It worried me whether we'll be able to eliminate it before than.<BR>But I had no idea we could eliminate the threat this clean and fast, I had to praise the military for this one!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-d" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>On top of that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT> may be gone, but the surroundings were badly <FONT color=#a82424>contaminated</FONT>, so there is a lot of damage. People who got in contact with the fluid from the Black Dragon's wound got ill or died... On top of that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-d" image="QM_dragonSycophant.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-e" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's... a big problem.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>It's a big problem <FONT color=#a82424>dragon followers</FONT> are freely acting out. Some of them are trying to do something bad using the Dragon's fluid.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-f" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What do you want me to do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Regardless of the fact, the ambient at Saint Haven isn't good. So if you're not too busy can you help me?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-f" image="QW_29.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-g" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>There was a tip that a group of dragon followers are trying to spread the disease by gathering contaminated materials from <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Overlord's Training Ground</FONT>. If we bring soldiers, it will be noisy and they will run away, so I hope you could quietly go over there and eliminate them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
