      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-2-next_quest" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes? What kind of job?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Oh... I just remembered after I thought of <FONT color=#a82424>Stas</FONT>, he had asked us to do a job. Do you want to do that job, too?</html>]]></talk_question>
